TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT t.VALID_YR, t.Payment_YR, t.AGT_CD, t.BU, t.CB_PAY_MONTHLY, t.PAY_START_DATE, t.PAY_END_DATE, t.CB_PAY_APPL_START_MONTH, TO_DATE(s.txt_key_value, 'yyyy-MM-dd') as OPER_CYCLE_DATE FROM RPT_CB_AGENT_MASTER t, IN_ETL_CONTROL s where s.txt_key_string = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' and TO_DATE(s.txt_key_value, 'yyyy-mm-dd') between t.PAY_START_DATE and t.PAY_END_DATE and t.qualifier_type = 'RECIPIENT' AND NVL(t.CB_PAY_MONTHLY, 0) <> 0 and t.Remove_Date = TO_DATE('2200-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd') and TO_DATE(s.txt_key_value, 'yyyy-mm-dd') = last_day(TO_DATE(s.txt_key_value, 'yyyy-mm-dd'))
